These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, apple, banana, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, polish, american, german
1. the polish is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person eating peach is the german##1
3. the american is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the person eating apple is on the left of the german##1
5. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lettuce | banana | apple | peach   |
| Nationality   | polish  | nigerian     | american   | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, card-games, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, skateboarding, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | card-games | chess | fishing | gardening    |
| Sport   | skateboarding    | basketball      | lacrosse | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, filmmaking, dancing, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, epic, romance
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | chess | dancing   | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | epic | romance | spy         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, adventure, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, volleyball, badminton, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | scientific | fantasy  | adventure      |
| Sport         | volleyball | weightlifting   | badminton | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, asparagus, cranberry, plum
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, bird, rat, chinchilla
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person eating plum is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | plum | cranberry | asparagus | garlic |
| Pet    | rabbit       | chinchilla | rat | bird     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, australian, german
4 different pets are kept: rat, cat, pony, bird
1. the chinese is on the far right##1
2. the german is on the left of the australian##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the australian##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | german | australian | canadian | chinese |
| Pet           | rat      | pony | bird | cat    |

