.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, country, rock, jazz
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, lizard, fish
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
3. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
5. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | country | techno | jazz  |
| Pet           | lizard | turtle | fish       | pony |

