.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, nurse, social-worker, teacher
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, helicopter, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person driving the train is the teacher##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the scientist##1
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the van is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | social-worker | scientist      | nurse | teacher |
| Transport   | van          | subway | helicopter     | train    |

