The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, train, car, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | thriller       | romance | scientific   |
| Transport     | train | car | scooter   | subway |

