.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, soy-milk, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, van, quad-bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | soy-milk  | coffee | water |
| Transport   | quad-bike | van | jet-ski          | bike    |

