.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, lemonade, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, pop, country, punk
1. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of country##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | coffee  | cola | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | country | punk           | pop   |

