.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, italian, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bike, quad-bike, jet-ski
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the british is on the left of the italian##1
4. the brazilian is the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | british | italian | dutch | brazilian   |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | taxi    | bike       | jet-ski |

 